description:
(Jeff & Sheri Easter Style)
Songwriters: The Brothers
Music performed by C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters Youtube Channel..
In this video, I'm taking a moment to thank God for His blessings on me. I've been through a lot this year, and I know that everything would not have been possible without His help. so I wanted to take a moment to say thank you Lord for all the good things in my life. From a stable relationship to good health, I know that without God's blessings, my life would be much harder. so I wanted to take this opportunity to just let you know how grateful I am for all of your blessings. Thank you Lord!
